你不配入主白宫
You don't deserve to be in the White House.

585
00:37:53,130 --> 00:37:54,880
你和你丈夫都不配
Neither you nor your husband.

586
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:03,500
我本想祝你一切安好  但我觉得你不需要
I'd wish you the best, but I don't think you'll need it.

587
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:06,880
我相当确定你在私人机构也能干得很好
I'm fairly certain you'll do very well in the private sector.

588
00:38:15,530 --> 00:38:18,200
我安排了周末跟简·戴维斯的会面
I've scheduled a meeting with Jane Davis for the end of the week.

589
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,290
很好
Good.

590
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:21,280
还有  我之前就想说的
Also, I was going to mention this earlier,

591
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:24,850
凯茜对艾丹·麦卡伦非常好奇
but Cathy's been very curious about Aidan Macallan.

592
00:38:25,220 --> 00:38:27,060
我已经转移了她的视线  但...
I've thrown her off the scent, but...

593
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:31,040
凯茜不是问题  而是麦卡伦
Cathy's not the problem. The problem is Macallan,

594
00:38:31,390 --> 00:38:34,210
还有那个纵容麦卡伦成为问题的人
and the person who allowed Macallan to become the problem.

595
00:38:40,100 --> 00:38:42,370
基金募集到了超过了八万
The foundation's raised over 80K.

596
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:46,670
安东尼于2016年3月15日进入1类捐赠名单
Anthony became status one on the donor list on March 15th, 2016.

597
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:49,580
莫雷蒂说那是她生命的最后一天
Moretti talked about it as, uh, the last day of her life

598
00:38:49,590 --> 00:38:50,770
之后又改了口
before she corrected herself.

599
00:38:50,770 --> 00:38:52,480
还有  时时刻刻陪着孩子
What else, spent every spare second with the kids.

600
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:53,610
他们还组装卡丁车来着
They were building a go-kart.

601
00:38:53,610 --> 00:38:54,610
本来就要完成了
They were pretty close to done.

602
00:38:54,610 --> 00:38:55,790
-好吧  -还有呢
- Okay. - I got more.

603
00:38:55,790 --> 00:38:58,350
-不用  我知道了  -你本想知道什么
- No, I got it. - What were you looking for?

604
00:38:58,350 --> 00:38:59,350
没什么
It's nothing.

605
00:39:03,150 --> 00:39:05,270
-好吧  -怎么了
- Okay. - What?

606
00:39:05,750 --> 00:39:07,900
你打算告诉我今天白宫发生了什么吗
You wanna tell me what happened in the White House today?

607
00:39:07,910 --> 00:39:09,380
不打算
No, I don't.

608
00:39:17,990 --> 00:39:19,820
好吧  我一直等着跟你说点事
All right, I've been waiting to say something,

609
00:39:19,830 --> 00:39:22,240
可我等得不想再等了
but I've waited and I don't want to wait anymore.

610
00:39:22,240 --> 00:39:25,090
帮我留意下白宫的工作吧  在新闻部
Consider me for a job at the White House, in comms.

611
00:39:28,540 --> 00:39:30,540
"去拿这个  帮我找那个  我要这个"
"Go get this. Find me that. I need this."

612
00:39:30,540 --> 00:39:31,530
我受够了
I'm tired of it.

613
00:39:31,530 --> 00:39:32,730
你不提出  就会被人命令
If you don't ask, you get asked.

614
00:39:32,730 --> 00:39:34,250
我开始意识到这点了
That's what I'm starting to realize.

615
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:35,570
我会帮你推荐的
I'll put a word in.

616
