Wants to do a story on Tony and the foundation.

634
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:33,750
他叫什么
What was his name?

635
00:41:01,730 --> 00:41:04,690
戴维斯暗示她能帮我们找到艾哈迈迪
Davis implied she could help us track down Ahmadi.

636
00:41:04,690 --> 00:41:07,100
我觉得我们该听听她要说什么
I think we should hear what she has to say.

637
00:41:08,730 --> 00:41:11,480
她有一种气质  对吧
She's got a quality about her, doesn't she?

638
00:41:12,170 --> 00:41:14,710
令人着迷又害怕
Attractive and terrifying.

639
00:41:15,510 --> 00:41:18,600
就像想抚摸红尾狐的冲动
Like the urge to pet a red tail fox.

640
