645
00:41:46,450 --> 00:41:50,150
讨论我们国家的危机和未来
to discuss the crisis and the future of our country.

646
00:41:50,150 --> 00:41:53,770
-你得受邀才能参加  -对  找他帮忙
- Well, you need to be invited to that. - Yes, let's get him in.

647
00:41:59,270 --> 00:42:01,770
我知道这很显然  但那总让我受触动
I know it's obvious, but it always strikes me.

648
00:42:01,970 --> 00:42:03,030
没有女人
No women.

649
