你知道我的态度
Well, you know my position.

654
00:42:18,890 --> 00:42:21,310
我完全支持女性参战
I'm all for women in combat.

655
00:44:04,670 --> 00:44:05,840
虚惊一场
False alarm...

656
00:44:13,460 --> 00:44:14,970
我很担心你
I was worried about you.

657
00:44:37,720 --> 00:44:39,890
我一直都担心你  克莱尔
I worry about you all the time, Claire.

658
00:44:45,560 --> 00:44:48,870
但我知道你不喜欢听这种话
But I know that's not the kind of thing you like to hear.

659
00:45:10,390 --> 00:45:12,780
马克  进来
Mark. Come in.

660
00:45:13,530 --> 00:45:15,990
-我们有很多要谈  -总统女士
- We have much to discuss. - Madam President.

661
00:45:17,420 --> 00:45:18,700
总统先生
Mr. President.

662
00:45:19,270 --> 00:45:20,930
我确信你知道
As I believe you know,

663
00:45:20,940 --> 00:45:25,320
我们昨天在白宫进行了演习
