"十月惊喜"赢得选举
with another so-called October surprise.

673
00:45:45,420 --> 00:45:48,990
-十月早就过了  -确实
- Well, we are way past October. - We certainly are.

674
00:45:51,850 --> 00:45:54,470
据我所知艾哈迈德·艾哈迈迪仍有威胁
I understand Ahmed Al Ahmadi is still a threat?

675
00:45:54,600 --> 00:45:58,250
是  但你也知道  他神出鬼没
Yes, but he's so elusive, as you know.

676
00:45:58,260 --> 00:46:00,130
很可惜你没能抓到他
It's a shame you weren't able to capture him.

677
00:46:00,540 --> 00:46:01,490
好吧
Well...

678
00:46:02,190 --> 00:46:04,320
我相信机会
I believe that the opportunity

679
00:46:04,320 --> 00:46:06,970
会自己跑到下任总统手中
