680
00:46:06,970 --> 00:46:08,700
无论总统是谁
whomever he may be.

681
00:46:09,530 --> 00:46:11,490
如果威尔·康威胜选
If Will Conway wins the office,

682
00:46:11,490 --> 00:46:13,810
我可以向你保证那会成为当务之急
I can assure you that'll be a top priority.

683
00:46:15,620 --> 00:46:17,490
这恐怖氛围得停止了
This terror has got to stop.

684
